itunes:summary:
Evan Hafer, Jarred Taylor, and Mat Best sit down with special guest former Navy Seal Eddie Gallagher describes his ordeal that brought his story to national attention in the United States after he was charged with war crimes. He was later pardoned by President Trump.  Here is his side of the story.
